<format xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="fNIF" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../schemas/format.xsd" display="show">
  <titleStmt>
    <title>NLP Interchange Format (NIF) for Linguistic Annotation of RDF Data</title>
    <abbr>NIF</abbr>
  </titleStmt>
  <keyword>annotation</keyword>
  <keyword>NLP</keyword>
  <keyword>linked data</keyword>
   <info type="description">
   <p>
    The NLP Interchange Format (NIF) is a standardized RDF/OWL-based format designed to facilitate the interoperability of Natural Language Processing (NLP) tools and resources on the Semantic Web.</p>
    <p>See:
      <a href="https://persistence.uni-leipzig.org/nlp2rdf/"> for a detailed description</a>.</p>
  </info>
